            <history-note id="DLM378476"><amended-provision>Section 56(1)(c)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>6 March 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM405674">section 8(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Customs and Excise Amendment Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 9).</history-note>
