            <history-note id="DLM379572"><amended-provision>Section 209(1)(d)</amended-provision> and <amended-provision>(e)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>22 February 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM333751">section 42(1)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Films, Videos, and Publications Classification Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 2).</history-note>
