            <history-note id="DLM379574"><amended-provision>Section 209(1A)</amended-provision> and <amended-provision>(1B)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>22 February 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM333751">section 42(3)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Films, Videos, and Publications Classification Amendment Act 2005</amending-leg> (2005 No 2).</history-note>
            <history-note id="DLM379575"><amended-provision>Section 209(3)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>6 March 2007</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM405924">section 20(2)</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Customs and Excise Amendment Act 2007</amending-leg> (2007 No 9).</history-note>
