        <heading>Notes</heading>
        <reprint.note>
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
          <heading>General</heading>
          <para>
            <text>This is an eprint of the Customs and Excise Act 1996. It incorporates all the amendments to the Act as at 24 September 2009. The list of amendments at the end of these notes specifies all the amendments incorporated into this eprint since 3 September 2007. Relevant provisions of any amending enactments that contain transitional, savings, or application provisions are also included, after the Principal enactment, in chronological order.</text>
          </para>
